open gimp
open COF_small_no_centre_text_2_titles.xcf
Select curved text layer then edit > cut
Script-Fu > Animation > Rotation Animation
Rotate times: 24
Motion: circular
Edit > Paste as > New Layer
Create a new layer group
Move curved text and original layer into group
Filters > Animation > Playback
Playback speed: 0.25
Frame rate: 10 fps

